name: TOXIC WORLD FIVE
description: Digitally altered photograph. 3398px by 5097px (72 ppi). 2112 A.D. Most of the world population has been wiped out by a pandemic which origin remains unknown. The rare survivors face countless dangers: infected water, rampant diseases, toxic fumes, and mutant insects, increasingly intelligent and deadly, which have taken over the world. No place is safe.
